dd tests for metrics collection\n\n**Verification**: Verify metrics are exported correctly and contain expected data\n\n---\n\n### Task 18: Implement concurrent safety tests\n- [ ] Add race detection to JWT tests\n- [ ] Implement `TestConcurrentGenerateToken` test\n- [ ] Implement `TestConcurrentValidateToken` test\n- [ ] Implement `TestConcurrentMixedOperations` test\n- [ ] Run tests with race detector enabled\n- [ ] Verify no race conditions detected\n\n**Verification**: Run `go test -race ./pkg/router -run TestJWTConcurrent` to verify thread safety\n\n---\n\n### Task 19: Add JWT health check endpoint\n- [ ] Update health check handlers to include JWT manager status\n- [ ] Verify JWT manager is initialized\n- [ ] Verify keys are available\n- [ ] Return JWT manager health status in /healthz/ready endpoint\n- [ ] Add tests for JWT health check\n\n**Verification**: Run `go test ./pkg/router -run TestJWTHealthCheck` to verify health check works\n\n---\n\n### Task 20: Final verification and cleanup\n- [ ] Run full JWT test suite\n  - [ ] `go test ./pkg/router -run TestJWT -v` - All JWT tests pass\n  - [ ] `go test ./pkg/router -run TestJWTMiddleware -v` - All middleware tests pass\n  - [ ] `go test ./pkg/router -run TestSecurityJWT -v` - All security tests pass\n- [ ] Run tests with race detector\n  - [ ] `go test -race ./pkg/router -run TestJWT` - No race conditions\n- [ ] Run benchmarks\n  - [ ] `go test ./pkg/router -bench=BenchmarkJWT` - Performance targets met\n- [ ] Run static analysis\n  - [ ] `go vet ./pkg/router` - No warnings\n  - [ ] `golangci-lint run ./pkg/router` - No linting issues (if available)\n- [ ] Verify code coverage\n  - [ ] `go test ./pkg/router -coverprofile=coverage.out` - Coverage meets requirements\n- [ ] Verify integration tests\n  - [ ] `go test ./pkg/router -run TestIntegrationJWT` - All integration tests pass\n- [ ] Review code for potential security issues\n- [ ] Verify error messages don't expose sensitive information\n- [ ] Verify logging doesn't expose private keys or tokens\n- [ ] Clean up any temporary test files or mock data\n\n**Verification**: All verification steps pass with no errors or warnings\n\n---\n\n## Summary\n\n**Total Tasks**: 20\n**Estimated Effort**: M (Medium) - 10-15 hours\n\n### Key Deliverables\n1. `jwt_middleware.go` - JWT authentication middleware\n2. `jwt_test.go` - Comprehensive JWT unit tests\n3. `jwt_security_test.go` - Security-focused JWT tests\n4. `jwt_integration_test.go` - End-to-end JWT flow tests\n5. Updated `errors.go` - JWT-specific error types\n6. Updated `handlers.go` - Token generation on session creation\n7. Updated `jwt.go` - Bug fixes and enhancements\n8. Enhanced logging for JWT operations\n9. Performance benchmarks for JWT operations\n10. Updated documentation with JWT authentication\n\n### Success Criteria\n- All tasks completed with tests passing\n- Code compiles without errors or warnings\n- Test coverage meets quality standards (target: 85%+ for JWT code)\n- Performance benchmarks meet requirements (P99 latency targets)\n- Security tests demonstrate robustness against common attacks\n- Documentation is complete and accurate\n- Integration with existing router components works correctly\n- No race conditions detected under concurrent load\n- Error handling provides clear, safe messages\n- Logging provides appropriate visibility without exposing secrets\n\n### Dependencies\n- Go 1.24+\n- `github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5` v5.2.0+\n- `github.com/gin-gonic/gin` v1.10.0+\n- `k8s.io/client-go` v0.34.1+\n- `k8s.io/klog/v2` v2.120.0+\n- Internal packages: `pkg/router`, `pkg/common/types`, `pkg/api`\n\n### Blocked By\n- None (design stage ST-3 completed)\n\n### Blocks\n- AR-009 (Router HTTP 反向代理核心) - Depends on JWT authentication for protected endpoints\n- AR-012 (Router session management) - Integration with JWT authentication\n- AR-013 (Router error handling) - JWT error handling integration\n- Production deployment with JWT authentication enabled\n\n### No